ree-dimensional unstructured DVS is proposed. Numerical results indicate\nthat, the present method is about one to two orders of magnitude faster than\nthe explicit conserved DUGKS method. The present method is proved to accurately\nand efficiently predict aerothermodynamic properties of hypersonic rarefied gas\nflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 03:39:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
