f the\ngeneralized Hilbert's Hotel. The generic experimental scheme illustrates the\nusefulness of structured beams in visualizing unusual mathematical concepts and\nalso for fractional vector beams driven fundamental and applied research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 10:34:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
